OL,3,CBlades condemn racist abuse after
OL,4,CHolgate red card
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Holgate shared a video
OL,7,Fmontage of some of the "constant
OL,8,Fracist abuse" he had received on
OL,9,Fsocial media, which included emojis of
OL,10,Fbananas, monkeys and gorillas - common
OL,11,Fracist imagery used to refer to black
OL,12,Fpeople - along with multiples
OL,13,Freferences to his race or use of
OL,14,Fracist slurs.
OL,16,FIn the post, he apologised for letting
OL,17,Fdown his teammates, the club and its
OL,18,Ffans, but said the last 48 hours had
OL,19,Fbeen "difficult to take".
