OL,3,CBlades condemn racist abuse after
OL,4,CHolgate red card
OL,6,F"As a sport and society we need to do
OL,7,Fmore and there needs to be
OL,8,Fconsequences for racism," he wrote.
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement that the club
OL,11,Fcondemned the abuse "in the strongest
OL,12,Fpossible terms".
OL,14,F"We will support Mason and applaud him
OL,15,Fbringing this to light on social
OL,16,Fmedia," they said.
OL,18,F"The club will work with relevant
OL,19,Fbodies to investigate. There is no
OL,20,Froom for racism in our game."
