OL,6,FThe Premier League added its support
OL,7,Ffor Holgate and the club, replying to
OL,8,Fthe Blades' post on X: "The Premier
OL,9,FLeague joins Sheffield United in
OL,10,Fcondemning the abhorrent racist abuse
OL,11,FMason Holgate has received online.J"We
OL,12,Fhave offered our full support to Mason
OL,13,Fand the club. We will work with the
OL,14,Frelevant authorities to help ensure
OL,15,Fany individuals identified and found
OL,16,Fguilty of discrimination face the
OL,17,Fstrongest possible consequences,
OL,18,Fincluding club bans and legal
OL,19,Fprosecution."
